datasets.name: 268c323c
datasets.query:
SELECT 
    u.name,
    u.title,
    u.role__c as role,
    o.opportunityid,
    o.ownerid,
    o.stagename,
    o.accountid,
    o.account_name,
    o.forecastcategory,
    o.description,
    o.createddate,
    o.closedate,
    o.amount
FROM main.dbdemos_aibi_sales_pipeline_review.opportunity o
LEFT JOIN main.dbdemos_aibi_sales_pipeline_review.user u on o.ownerid = u.id
